# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Paper: include only the NCC paradigm article
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Exclude other authors' solo work
paper/papers/solo_alizée/

# Exclude old paper infrastructure (Overleaf clone, old scripts)
paper/.git/
paper/.gitignore
paper/README.md
paper/results/
paper/src/
paper/scripts/
paper/requirements.txt
paper/papers/bibliography/
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/README.md

# Exclude superseded tex files (main.tex is the canonical version)
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/latex/CCF_paradigm_NCC.tex
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/latex/CCF_paradigm_NCC_redux.tex
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/latex/CCF_paradigm_NCC_SI.tex
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/latex/CCF.bib

# Exclude compiled PDFs (regenerable from tex)
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/latex/*.pdf

# Exclude generated CSV/JSON intermediates (regenerable from scripts)
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/tables/*.csv
paper/papers/CCF_paradigm/tables/*.json

# Always ignore pycache
__pycache__/
